Package jchess.cache

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoardCache
    This is a cache class that is responsible to store all details regarding a Chess-board.
    BoardData
    This is a data class to that stores Chess-board related details in the cache.
    BoardDataFactory
    Factory class for BoardData.
    BoardMapping
    This class holds Board mapping.
    CacheManager
    This class is responsbile to load Board details from secondary storage (DB or File).
    Path
    This is a data class to store "Path or Direction" related details in cache.
    PieceData
    This is a data class to store "Piece" related details in cache.
    PlayerData
    This is a data class to store "Player" related details in cache.
    PlayerPieceMapping
    This is a data class that keeps information about which pieces are set to players and on what positions they have to be placed.
    PositionData
    This is a data class to store "Position" related details in cache.
    Quadrilateral
    This class is specific for figures with four vertexes.
    RuleData
    This is a data class to store "Rule" related details in cache.
